    %%%
    % Applies a parsing function to each string in a list of strings
    %
    % Example usage:
    % In: ["  _&Hello there...! General Kenobi!!! %100 "]
    % Out: ["hello there general kenobi 100"] if Parser = fun {$ StrLine} {RemoveEmptySpace {ParseLine Str_Line}} end
    %
